'''ProTV''' is an extensible [[Special:MyLanguage/Video_players|video player]]. Supporting a variety of customizable plugins such as Media Controls, Playlists, Queues, 360 Skybox Video, VoteSkip, and [[Community:AudioLink|AudioLink]] integration. It also comes with native support for livestreams like [[Community:VRCDN|VRCDN]] and on Quest.

== Setup ==
Everyone can download ProTV with the [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat_Creator_Companion|Creator Companion]] and add it to projects then a prefab can be dragged into worlds and the video will work. It is also possible to put a video into it so you can have default music playing when the tv is loaded.

Speakers can be made louder and with more range or even made so audio is heard everywhere.

